    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/extras/9eaceb0f91c8f6666de081b75d76831f.poster.avif?t=1772468974\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/extras/9eaceb0f91c8f6666de081b75d76831f.webm?t=1772468974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/extras/9eaceb0f91c8f6666de081b75d76831f.mp4?t=1772468974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tower Defense meets Idle Clicker</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a Tower Defense x Idle Clicker game set inside the Crayon Empire. Each new level you progress will award you Points that can be used in the Shop to purchase new tower placement spots, new weapon types and more. Build up your defenses, let the game play out then come back to upgrade and unlock new opportunities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/extras/e123adbb7b944e83fe1dac55d3056388.poster.avif?t=1772468974\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/extras/e123adbb7b944e83fe1dac55d3056388.webm?t=1772468974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/extras/e123adbb7b944e83fe1dac55d3056388.mp4?t=1772468974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Idle Special</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you let the game idle in the background, the &quot;Idle Special&quot; bar will slowly fill up. When it is fully ready, click that button! It will unleash a powerful attack on all the unsuspecting enemies trying to harm your base. Impatient and can't wait for it to fill up? Click click click and fill it in faster! Might unleash even powerful attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/extras/499fde7606e907fb78d793c3a1772157.poster.avif?t=1772468974\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/extras/499fde7606e907fb78d793c3a1772157.webm?t=1772468974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/extras/499fde7606e907fb78d793c3a1772157.mp4?t=1772468974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Auto Defenses Deployed</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Got something else to take care of? Step away and let the game handle your defenses for you! Your base and the weapons you placed will slowly level up and upgrade over time allowing your defenses to keep up advancing stronger enemy types.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/extras/97e8bb3dad07dc791c9412179209145e.poster.avif?t=1772468974\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/extras/97e8bb3dad07dc791c9412179209145e.webm?t=1772468974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264140/extras/97e8bb3dad07dc791c9412179209145e.mp4?t=1772468974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 20 different custom Maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 different Game Modes: Idle and Death</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music Player</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cloud Saves</p></li></ul>",
